dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Rock_Zoning_2014.gdb'.[Zoning in Rock County is by Town authority. This feature class represents the zoning districts in Rock County as assigned by the towns and disseminated to the County. It should be used in conjunction with the Zoning feature class, and the ZoningLookUp and the ZoningOverlayLookUp tables.
